      "review_summary": "The PR marks manual cron completions, preserves one-shot jobs and retry/alert counters for manual runs, adds `lastRunWasManual` to cron state/protocol, and expands cron regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +74, Tests +751. Total +825 across 8 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. The current PR merge-ref CI reproduces the remaining regression in `src/cron/service.runs-one-shot-main-job-disables-it.test.ts`: two one-shot disabled-heartbeat tests fail after due completions skip scheduled-state handling.",
